dia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 506, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\", \"score\": 0.7116029751916966, \"rank\": 0.4004728477648725, \"text\": \"Munich\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Munich\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At those Olympics, the Palestinian militant group known as Black September murdered 11 Israeli competitors as well as one German police officer.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9999983460968486, \"rank\": 1.6481452655141356e-06, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}, {\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.5886166122761546, \"rank\": 0.6920134872523604, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 676, \"end\": 682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9807138138797162, \"rank\": 0.01966194267979841, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old Hadid and Adidas were both met swiftly with public backlash, including accusations of antisemitism.\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Guess who the face of their campaign is?\\\"\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"the official X account for Israelposted.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Bella Hadid, a half-Palestinian model who has a history of spreading antisemitism and calling for violence against Israelis and Jews.\\\"\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bella Hadid\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q4610556\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bella_Hadid\"}, {\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"score\": 0.9999960460830558, \"rank\": 3.953686153850486e-06, \"text\": \"Israelis\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israelis\"}, {\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9977643850900717, \"rank\": 0.0022341572707534826, \"text\": \"Jews\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For Adidas to pick a vocal anti-Israel model to recall this dark Olympics is either a massive oversight or intentionally inflammatory,\\\" the American Jewish Committeewrote on X.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9308542050595617e-16, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}, {\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anti-Zionism\", \"score\": 0.9999201321647962, \"rank\": 7.987421453810331e-05, \"text\": \"anti-Israel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anti-Zionism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anti-Zionism\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Neither is acceptable.\\\"\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid in the past has spoken out against Israel's occupation ofPalestineas well as the Israeli military's onslaught in Gaza in retaliation for Hamas's 7 October attacks.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1283, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.99677037428348e-15, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3533334724994686e-38, \"text\": \"Israeli military\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"score\": 0.999849362560656, \"rank\": 0.00015066013429773152, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_Strip\"}, {\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8294853169341326e-18, \"text\": \"Hamas\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has repeatedly refuted accusations that she is antisemitic.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, Adidas pulled the ad with Hadid and pledged to revise the remainder of the SL72 marketing campaign, saying the company did not intend to make any connections \\\"to tragic historical events\\\".\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1490, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9308542050595617e-16, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And late Monday, Hadid joined the chorus of people criticizing Adidas.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9308542050595617e-16, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am shocked, I am upset, and I am disappointed in the lack of sensitivity that went into this campaign,\\\" Hadid wrote in a statement posted on Instagram.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1896, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 0.9999999873548405, \"rank\": 1.2645135941244374e-08, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hadid, who was born in 1996, said she had never learned about \\\"the historical connection to the atrocious events in 1972\\\".\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said she would \\\"never knowingly engage with any art or work that is linked to a horrific tragedy of any kind\\\".\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My team should have known,\\\" Hadid added.\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Adidas should have known, and I should have done more research so that I too would have known and understood, and spoken up.\\\"\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Hadid's supporters haveaccusedAdidas of racism for linking Hadid to terrorism because of her ethnic background.\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And many pro-Palestinian activists have urged people to boycott Adidas.\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2505, \"end\": 2511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9308542050595617e-16, \"text\": \"Adidas\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adidas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adidas on 21 July also publiclyapologizedto Hadid and others who participated in the botched campaign, saying the company \\\"made an unintentional mistake\\\" and expressing regret \\\"for any negative impact\\\".\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2716, \"entities\": []}]}"